---
title: Indian Apricot-Glazed Chickpea Tacos with Cucumber, Mint & Roasted Cashews
description: Wow, there’s a lot being packed into these tacos, they might explode! The sweet apricot glaze counterbalances the North Indian spices of the chickpeas. Not to mention the cooling relief of the mint and cucumber. We even squeezed in some nutty goodness to really make this dish go off with a bang!
